{"tid":2240429,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【iPhone年年半價換新？】蘋果香港註冊「iPhone for Life」商標 估計為Upgrade換新機計劃","createTime":"2020-10-12T15:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T16:19:59.000Z","uid":372829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0281ba854015a6db33ffac2699957ebb899eb1","tid":2240429,"uid":372829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"蘋果（Apple）早已於美國、中國兩地推出「iPhone 年年換新計劃」（iPhone Upgrade Program ），惟香港的果迷就仍然未能享受此Upgrade新iPhone的計劃。不過綜合外媒最新發現，蘋果早前在香港註冊「iPhone for Life」的商標，估計為 iPhone Upgrade Program 在香港地區採用的名稱！<br />\n <br />\n外媒報道指，蘋果今年 4 月在本港申請「iPhone for Life」的商標專利，編號為 305380876，說明其包含零售通路服務等的 35 類項目，以及包含金融相關的 36 類項目。而外界預料，該名稱其實為 iPhone 年年換新計劃。<br />\n<br />\n該iPhone 年年換新計劃是2015 年在美國推出的一個升級換購新iPhone項目，只要在實體 Apple Store 買新 iPhone 時，加購 AppleCare+，就可以在買入手機後的第 10 個月起到第 13 個月末，以原設備零售價格50%的折抵優惠升級換購新iPhone。隨後再於發布iPhone 7及iPhone 7 Plus之際，在中國市場推出。<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2773247/【iPhone年年半價換新？】蘋果香港註冊「iPhone%20for%20Life」商標%20%20%20估計為Upgrade換新機計劃?mtc=20040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2773247%2F%E3%80%90iPhone%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%83%B9%E6%8F%9B%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E3%80%8CiPhone%2520for%2520Life%E3%80%8D%E5%95%86%E6%A8%99%2520%2520%2520%E4%BC%B0%E8%A8%88%E7%82%BAUpgrade%E6%8F%9B%E6%96%B0%E6%A9%9F%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%3Fmtc%3D20040&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V8QVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=d02e0b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2773247/【iPhone年年半價換新？】蘋果香港註冊「iPhone%20for%20Life」商標%20%20%20估計為Upgrade換新機計劃?mtc=20040</a>"},{"pid":"eb19013912f8352a94d8057693d3c78f2141f233","tid":2240429,"uid":372829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"逼死你用Apple用到瓜老襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src